data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Hampton! This meticulously maintained 3-bed, 2.5-bath gem, built in 2020, boasts an inviting open concept design. Upstairs, you'll find spacious bedrooms, including a huge master retreat with his and her closets. Enjoy the perfect blend of comfort and style with generously sized living spaces. Your ideal home sweet home awaits! Seller is offering $5000 concession with full-priced offer.
